{"tid":419009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國務院官網改版　介紹台灣頁面國旗消失了","createTime":"2017-09-30T05:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T10:51:56.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"53b370d6280c84990e183d594d544115c1e52082","tid":419009,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"美國務院官網改版　介紹台灣頁面國旗消失了<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170930/1214125/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170930%2F1214125%2F&d=9gzO7v1m18dUcokXBQhKaKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=76b8afd4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170930/1214125/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院官網（<a href=\"http://www.state.gov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov&d=9gzO7v1m18dUcokXBQhKaKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=370e7a8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.state.gov</a>）最近改版，卻被媒體發現，原本介紹台灣的頁面，中華民國國旗竟然消失不見。<br />\n<br />\n中央社報導，川普上任後，國務院及白宮官網依照慣例進行更改，國務院官網在5月底時仍可看見台灣的地理位置圖及中華民國國旗。不過，青天滿地紅國旗圖案最近卻消失不見，只留下台灣地圖。<br />\n<br />\n國務院東亞暨太平洋事務局發言人崔葛瑞斯（Grace Choi）對此回復表示，美國的政策沒有改變，也就是：美國信守基於美中「三個公報」與「台灣關係法」的「一中政策」。但未說明為何中華民國國旗不見頁面上。<br />\n<br />\n報導同時指出，川普上任後，貿易代表署的網頁也有改變，關於台灣的介紹，仍保有變為圓形圖案的中華民國國旗。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"2a05d20fc48464348d99e94e2f33fa11e121dc60","tid":419009,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd18a2840384644a1f0f278b20115f6be389fb2a","tid":419009,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"Trump是生意佬，北韓問題要支共幫手"},{"pid":"fec0fc85554c62d8708737695732aeb3e7577340","tid":419009,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T10:46:52.000Z","msg":"台狗：美爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼不是連去支那（中華人民共和國）"},{"pid":"7ceb99c6039dc8cb812859ce2bd7dd3e3c882a69","tid":419009,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n川普今天早上在8時50分左右親自在推特（Twitter）上發文表示，「台灣總統今天打電話給我，祝賀我當選總統。謝謝你！」（The President of Taiwan CALLED ME today to wish me congratulations on winning the Presidency. Thank you!）"}]}